{"tid":2292440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大一戰 除左慘情 還有巨型人血饅頭 大家一定要記得","createTime":"2020-11-19T13:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T03:28:32.000Z","uid":162456,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9807f7a8ae9a3e8877b5f463415a681f28c2d8","tid":2292440,"uid":162456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dirSjuhYqxU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdirSjuhYqxU&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=c133856d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dirSjuhYqxU</a><br />\n<br />\n蛋蛋俱樂部前高登記者崔X蛋用前媒體記者被捕為名呃真香港人保釋金<br />\n一定要睇晒條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呃錢師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條片佢有講憑自己呃返嚟既錢鍾意點用就點用 唔關人事唔洗同人交代<br />\n<br />\n我代表所有畀佢呃錢的前課金苦主聯盟同大家講！！<br />\n所有盲撐崔X蛋既都係港豬！！<br />\n人血崔X蛋呃左甘大筆錢本來可以幫到好多手足！！<br />\n上庭打官司交學費做到好多野！！<br />\n宜家畀佢袋撚哂！！！<br />\n手足POLY一戰斷手斷腳都無錢醫！幾多個手足係狗屋畀狗打完出到黎仲要面臨不斷加罪名！<br />\n手足為香港付出左甘多你地系咪唔撚記得哂？！<br />\n仲助長偽黃食人血饅頭對吾對得住班打生打死既手足！？<br />\n<br />\n吾該大家睇清楚條人血PK！<br />\n幫手share出去！<br />\n除非你地當手足CONDOM！！"},{"pid":"ae3a2d227e60e1e47cc3cb2b63d29f579bfa5f46","tid":2292440,"uid":162456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"204bc97d7482246706361ae0414a9afcb85f70e6","tid":2292440,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"你自己推飽佢啦"},{"pid":"00eeddb4690728e00cac3669f5cdb85a81bad429","tid":2292440,"uid":162456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83a443502dd2004dbd0ed50bee1df516d136ebb9","tid":2292440,"uid":162456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4932011e11bf62fa31988c2a90e6ccf6e059d5d","tid":2292440,"uid":162456,"like":0